
#	Configuration file for Soundwave setup
#       puts a sine wave perturbation in density, speed, and pressure
#       on the grid along x, y, or z axis

REQUIRES Driver
REQUIRES physics/Hydro

D orientation  1/2/3 -- sine wave is oriented along x/y/z axis
D wavelength   period of the sine wave
D rho_init     undisturbed initial density
D perturb_amp  fractional amplitude of sine wave disturbance
D cs           adiabatic soundspeed of a small-amplitude soundwave, evaluated 
D &            at the unperturbed background state
 

PARAMETER orientation	INTEGER 1
PARAMETER wavelength	REAL	1.
PARAMETER rho_init	REAL	1.
PARAMETER perturb_amp	REAL	0.1
PARAMETER cs  	REAL	1.



